                                    <img src="resources/images/crowd.svg">
                                    <h3>Everyone needs life insurance</h3>
                                    <p style="display: none;">For most people, life insurance is a necessity. But if you have sizable assets and no debt, or if you have no dependents or heirs you want to provide for, you are probably better off "self-insuring.” Save enough to cover your final expenses and you won't need life insurance under the conditions we've outlined.</p>
