                                    <img src="resources/images/heart.svg">
                                    <h3>I don't need to worry about my health for life insurance</h3>
                                    <p style="display: none;">Insurance companies gauge the risk of all applicants. High risk to the insurer means high premiums, often for low coverage policies. Fit individuals have a very high likelihood of getting the best price and the most coverage, as health markers usually indicate a long and enjoyable life span.</p>
                                    <a href="#" class="secondary">Read More</a>
