                                    <h3>Everyone should buy term and invest the difference</h3>
                                    <p style="display: none;">Buying term life insurance and investing funds elsewhere isn’t right for everyone. Providing for a special needs child or covering estate taxes are two typical reasons to have permanent insurance.</p>
                                    <a href="#" class="secondary">Read More</a>
                                </div>
