                                    <img src="resources/images/money.svg">
                                    <h3>I don't need life insurance, I'll just invest my money</h3>
                                    <p style="display: none;">There is a point in time for some people where investments have amassed enough volume that they don't need life insurance any longer. For most younger Americans, accumulated savings and investments would do little more than cover final expenses. If your investments do not meet the needs of your loved ones, you may need life insurance.</p>
